projects.title: PassWatch
projects.description: A password breach scanner with Firebase authentication, real-time history tracking. Features password strength analysis, secure generator, crack time estimation, and breach detection with k-anonymity for privacy.

projects.title: Autism Predictor
projects.description: A machine learning model deployed using Streamlit to predict whether a person has autism based on given input features.

projects.title: PDF Extractor
projects.description: This is a minimal MVP to extract text from PDFs and images and provide basic engagement suggestions.

responsibilities: I'm currently tasked with assisting the main developer team in data pre-processing and ELT(Extract-Transform-Load) pipeline.

about.bio:
Hello! I'm passionate about building digital solutions that make a difference. My journey into software development began with curiosity and has evolved into a deep love for crafting elegant code and intuitive user experiences. Whether it's frontend magic or backend logic, I find joy in solving problems one line at a time.

Fast-forward to today, and I'm currently working at a company where I'm building quality software solutions and expanding my horizons. Recently, I've developed a strong inclination towards data science and machine learning, diving into the fascinating world of algorithms that can learn and adapt.
